    <title>制作个人博客过程和出现问题</title>
    <url>/2023/06/20/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>以下是我自己做博客的详细过程，尽量写的简单一点，希望可以帮到自己回忆。<br>博客框架版本:hexo 6.3.0<br>主题:next </p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h3 id="第一步-注册GitHub"><a href="#第一步-注册GitHub" class="headerlink" title="第一步 注册GitHub:"></a>第一步 注册GitHub:</h3><p>点击进入<a href="https://github.com/" title="Github">Github官网</a><br>注册很简单，去浏览器搜索，只需要按照他的填，就能成功，听说别的浏览器不行，我这边用的是微软的浏览器，应该都能注册成功，然后就是绑定邮箱了，这里要注意！！！！我之前找很久都 没有找到settings,点击右上角头像就可以看到，进入设置界面（settings）后，点击Emails（邮箱）进行绑定。<br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E9%82%AE%E7%AE%B1%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A.png" alt="这是图片" title="邮箱绑定"><br>在Github的主页，右上角有个“+”，点击New repository，可以创建一个仓库<br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93.png" alt="这是图片" title="创建仓库"><br>现在可以先不用创建，后面hexo绑定到GitHub后再创建</p>
<h3 id="第二步-安装git"><a href="#第二步-安装git" class="headerlink" title="第二步 安装git:"></a>第二步 安装git:</h3><p>点击进入<a href="https://git-scm.com/" title="git">git官网</a>，下载最新版版本的git，我现在用的是2.41.0版本的。<br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit1.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git1.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit2.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git2.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit3.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git3.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit4.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git4.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit5.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git5.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit6.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git6.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit7.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git7.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit8.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git8.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit9.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git9.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit10.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git10.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit11.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git11.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit12.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git12.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit13.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git13.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit14.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git14.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit15.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git15.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit16.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git16.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit17.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git17.png"><br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDgit18.png" alt="这是图片" title="下载git18.png"><br>因为我电脑是已经安装了的，所以有些和新安装的可能不同，我安装时少了选择安装路径这条，要是对不上的话，可以先点next，勾选的这些东西应该是对的上的，先勾选上，只是顺序可能不一样。<br>安装成功后，打开git bash，右键桌面也有。<br>输入：git<br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5git.png" alt="这是图片" title="输入git"><br>回车得到下图：<br><img src="/images/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5git%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C.png" alt="这是图片" title="输入git结果"><br>恭喜你，安装成功！！</p>
